<% content_for(:title, "World of Prescriptions" ) %>

    <div class="body_col col-xs-6 col-md-3">
      <%= link_to image_tag("prescription.jpg", :class=>"image_box img-responsive img-thumbnail"), prescriptions_path %>
      <h3>Manage Prescriptions</h3>
      <p>Add new prescriptions, view all current prescriptions</p>
    </div>

    <div class="body_col col-xs-6 col-md-3">
      <%= link_to image_tag("drug.jpg", :class=>"image_box img-responsive img-thumbnail"), drugs_path %>
      <h3>Manage Drugs</h3>
      <p>Add and view all drugs in your library. These will be added to your prescriptions.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="body_col col-xs-6 col-md-3">
      <%= link_to image_tag("cost.jpg", :class=>"image_box img-responsive img-thumbnail"), drugs_path %>
      <h3>Manage costs</h3>
      <p>Look at your totals for the donut hole and how much you have spent on prescriptions year to date.</p>
    </div>

    <aside class="col-xs-6 col-md-3 ">
      <div class="row aside_box">
        <p>Donut Hole Remaining:</p>
        <p>$1,326.00</p>
      </div>
      <div class="row aside_box">
        <p>Out of Pocket YTD:</p>
        <p>$345.00</p>
      </div>
      <div class="row aside_box2">
        <p>Utilize this tool to manage your monthly prescriptions. It is challenging to understand the donut hole and to understand
            the current yearly cost. This tool allows you to put in a monthly cost to your donut hole from your statement and the
            tool will keep track of the yearly running total for the donut hole and your total prescriptions cost you have paid.
            For more on the donut hole gap from the government website click here <a href="http://www.medicare.gov/part-d/costs/coverage-gap/part-d-coverage-gap.html">Medicare.gov</a></p>
      </div
    </aside>



